{"_path":"/maps/_person/technology/gary-marcus","_dir":"technology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Gary Marcus","description":"认知科学家、AI 研究者、作家，以批判性视角关注人工智能发展","original_path":"content/6.maps/_person/gary-marcus.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gary Marcus 是认知科学家、AI 研究者、企业家和作家。他是纽约大学心理学与神经科学荣誉教授，曾创立机器学习公司 Geometric Intelligence（后被 Uber 收购），并创立了机器人公司 Robust.AI。他以对当前 AI 技术路径的批判性观点而闻名，主张结合深度学习与符号推理的混合方法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要观点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要观点？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对深度学习局限性的批判"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"认为当前大语言模型本质上是「高级自动补全」，缺乏真正的理解和推理能力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"指出深度学习在数据效率、泛化能力和可解释性方面存在根本性缺陷"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主张「深度学习撞墙了」(Deep Learning is Hitting a Wall)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对 AI 安全的关注"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关注 AI 竞赛中的安全风险，特别是当商业利益凌驾于安全考量之上时"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提出 p(doom) 评估会因企业鲁莽行为而上升"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"批评 OpenAI、xAI 等公司在安全措施上的倒退"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合 AI 架构倡导者"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主张将神经网络的感知能力与符号系统的推理能力结合"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"认为通往 AGI 需要更结构化的知识表示和因果推理能力"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"代表作品"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代表作品？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《重启 AI》（Rebooting AI，2019）- 与 Ernest Davis 合著，探讨构建可信 AI 的路径"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《代数思维》（The Algebraic Mind，2001）- 关于认知科学的早期著作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《未来的面孔》（Guitar Zero，2012）- 关于音乐学习的科普作品"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"媒体活动"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"媒体活动？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"活跃于 Substack（Marcus on AI）和 X/Twitter，定期评论 AI 行业动态"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"曾与 Yann LeCun 等深度学习先驱公开辩论 AI 发展路径"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"参与美国国会关于 AI 监管的听证会"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"个人与影响"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"个人与影响？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2026 年 2 月，Gary Marcus 在母亲 Marilyn (Molly) Marcus 突然离世后，写下了一篇感人至深的悼念文章。\n他回顾了母亲作为治疗师和社会工作者的一生，以及从她身上学到的人生准则：\n人皆有共通之处、关注整个世界、每个生命都重要、金钱不是唯一变量、为自己而写作、默默支持所爱之人。\n这些人文价值观深刻影响了 Gary 对 AI 发展路径的思考，特别是他对 AI 安全和社会责任的关切。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://garymarcus.substack.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gary Marcus Substack"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gary_Marcus","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wikipedia - Gary Marcus"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/marilyn-molly-marcus-1942-2026","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"悼念母亲 Marilyn (Molly) Marcus"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:technology:gary-marcus.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/technology/gary-marcus.md","_stem":"6.maps/_person/technology/gary-marcus","_extension":"md"}